race.comment: BAD BOY LEROY (4) boasts a strong record this journey here with four wins and three minors from eight tries. Scored by 1.5 lengths last time (18.25) in a Grade 5 over 320m at this track. Expected to go close. COAL (1) turned in a solid run last start over 401m at this track finishing 5th and beaten only 2.5 lengths (23.85). Expected to give a good account. BUGATTI ROCKS (2) finished third (18.81) two back at this track but out of the placings last time when 6th there. Solid record here at the distance winning three races. One of the main contenders. CHRIS WHIT (6) is worth some thought after placing at this track and distance last start.
